data.description: SELLER WILLING TO CONTRIBUTE UP TO $11k TOWARD BUYER CLOSING COSTS/PRE-PAIDS**Check out this gem of a home that offers all you need and more! Tucked away on a spacious 1/3-acre lot, this place offers you the freedom you deserve with NO pesky HOA rules to worry about. The real highlight? A fantastic Fiberglass chlorine pool that was recently resealed, which is perfect for cooling off during those hot summer days. Inside, you'll find a place that's been taken care of. The tile throughout keeps things low maintenance, which is just what you need after a long day's work. The kitchen? It's a real treat with gleaming granite countertops and a suite of stainless-steel appliances that make you feel right at home. The kitchen features a breakfast bar which perfect for those quick morning meals. Never miss a beat from the kitchen as it overlooks the kitchen and living room. And don't forget about the practical perks – a NEW water heater ensures your showers are never cold, both bathrooms were recently remodeled and the fenced backyard gives you a private space to relax or let the dog run wild. The exterior's had a fresh coat of paint, making this home shine even brighter. Plus, there's an exterior shed – just the spot for stashing your tools or extra gear. So, if you're looking for a place that's got heart, space, and all the comforts you need, come see this beauty and live life the way you want it.
